{"tid":634053,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實我已開始崩潰","createTime":"2018-04-19T00:59:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-02T00:41:40.000Z","uid":169676,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"7a690cd85cd7e8807a2a6c7b91d8e52d0affe5c9","tid":634053,"uid":169676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T00:59:11.000Z","msg":"我呢件事對比個啲被分手、出軌呀之類嘅post<br />\n真係算微不足道<br />\n好小兒科<br />\n算得啲咩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過我真係感覺到<br />\n係好真實好實在嘅感覺嚟<br />\n我無得否認呢樣嘢<br />\n而我控制唔到<br />\n不斷釋放呢種感覺出嚟<br />\n就好似一種signal<br />\n點都要將呢個訊號傳遞畀個女仔<br />\n好想畀佢知道我對佢感覺係點樣<br />\n<br />\n但我真係無辦法中斷呢啲signal<br />\n根本就無一個開關掣可以畀我熄咗佢<br />\n我一路釋放 一路就自己接收返<br />\n然後越積越多<br />\n就快到咗無法再容納嘅底步<br />\n<br />\n我就嚟爆啦<br />\n我好想嗌到失哂聲大喊一場<br />\n無奈嘅係我連呢樣嘢都無法做到<br />\n係現實生活中<br />\n我要將呢啲失落嘅情緒收埋起嚟<br />\n公司有人 屋企又有人<br />\n我可以點樣嗌？點樣喊出聲而無人知道？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4c2cf53695ccbce436b0c3513ea87e947fb3306","tid":634053,"uid":51701,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T01:02:07.000Z","msg":"上山鳩叫<br />\n<br />\n請一日假<br />\n<br />\n去叫雞<br />\n<br />\n去做運動"},{"pid":"dc589da4c64b820ab891c522dc34ac780a51c569","tid":634053,"uid":4525,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T01:03:34.000Z","msg":"當面講囉<br />\n毒撚發情最可怕"},{"pid":"0efad6daebe4588b032764c0952a78e0fb1b3ad1","tid":634053,"uid":123774,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T01:04:06.000Z","msg":"好痴漢feel <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4460d6c84064e2f59668acfe10646011ab4db834","tid":634053,"uid":169676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T01:10:56.000Z","msg":"我都覺得自己失哂理性<br />\n成個人好痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji